# TASK::OPEN_PATROL_ROUTE

## Summary
Opens up a empty route so that nodes and links can be added

## Parameters
* **STRING** routeName:
This must be prefixed with miss_ to be valid.
eg "miss_Desert1"

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
